From 993436b5a4d2518656e6e1b49f8e400b1c791ed9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Wed, 27 May 2026 13:13:38 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Probe PDF stream handoff

The PDF stream knocked on Chrome's door,
And brought a browser through the floor.
It reached the linker, bold and bright,
Then proved this path is far too wide.
